sequenceDiagram
    participant W as Workload
    participant IDP as Identity Provider
    participant V as Verifier
    note over W, V: Credential Acquisition Phase
    W->>+W: Generate Key
    W->>+W: Create Credential Request<br/>using Key
    W->>+W: Create Quote<br/> using Credential Request
    W->>+IDP: Request Credential<br/>with Quote as Evidence
    IDP->>+V: Forward Quote<br/>from Credential Request
    V->>+IDP: Attestation<br/>Results
    IDP->>+IDP: Convert Attestation Results<br/>to Credential Attributes
    IDP->>+IDP: Create and Sign Credential<br/>from Credential Request<br/>and Credential Attributes
    IDP->>+W: Credential
